data.description: This delightful home is located in beautiful Old Mill Branch. This is the ''happening'' area with Tinseltown on the north and the St Johns Town Center to the south. So many great places to shop, so many fabulous restaurants, lots of areas of employment at Deerwood Park and the nearby Southpoint and Baymeadows business districts. You'll love this home. It features a formal living and dining areas, a huge master suite, open kitchen, breakfast and family room. The screened patio overlooks a pretty, just-the-right-size backyard- there's plenty of space for play equipment and outdoor entertaining. Almost 500sq ft. of pavers added to backyard.
data.whatILove: Neighborhood has pool and hot tub with a playground.
